    "description": "Grow your career with MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Front Office Manager for our Tiruchirappalli team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited:\nMakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited!",
